duties_responsibilities.duty: Lead and support implementation and upgrade projects for SAP Transportation Management.
Provide technical services for transportation management processes within SAP TM.
Configure and customize transportation management processes aligned with business requirements.
Analyze and evaluate as-is business processes to design to-be processes for transportation management.
Collaborate with SAP and functional teams to resolve technical issues and enhance system performance.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related field (Master's preferred)
